<% provide(:title, 'и©•дѕЎеѕ…гЃЎдїіеЏҐ') %>
<h1>и©•дѕЎеѕ…гЃЎдїіеЏҐ</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
    <% if @haikus.any? %>
      <%= will_paginate @haikus %>
      <% @haikus.each do |haiku| %>
        <div class="haiku-card">
          <p class="haiku-card__body">
            <%= link_to haiku.body, haiku %>
          </p>
          <p class="haiku-card__meta">
            <span class="haiku-card__kigo">
              <%= haiku.kigo %>
            </span>
            <span class="haiku-card__author">
              <%= haiku.user.name %>
            </span>
            <span class="haiku-card__time">
              <%= l haiku.created_at,
                  format: :short %>
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <%= will_paginate @haikus %>
    <% else %>
      <p>и©•дѕЎеѕ…гЃЎгЃ®дїіеЏҐгЃЇгЃ‚г‚ЉгЃѕгЃ›г‚“гЂ‚</p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
